🔴 13. Payment Gateway

      Examples:
          Razorpay
          Stripe
          PayPal
    Flow:
        
        🔄 Step-by-Step Workflow
        🔹 1. User Clicks Pay Button
        ✅ English:
        
        Customer clicks “Pay Now” on your website/app.
        
        ✅ Tamil:
        
        User “Pay Now” button click பண்ணுவார்.
        
        🔹 2. Order Creation (Backend)
        ✅ English:
        
        Your backend creates an order using Razorpay API.
        
        👉 Important:
        
        amount
        currency
        order_id
        Example (PHP concept):
        $order = $api->order->create([
          'amount' => 50000, // ₹500
          'currency' => 'INR'
        ]);
        ✅ Tamil:
        
        Backend-ல் Razorpay API மூலம் order create பண்ணுவோம்
        
        👉 இதில்:
        
        amount
        currency
        order id
        🔹 3. Send Order ID to Frontend
        ✅ English:
        
        Backend sends the order_id to frontend (UI).
        
        ✅ Tamil:
        
        Backend → frontend-க்கு order_id அனுப்பும்
        
        🔹 4. Open Razorpay Checkout
        ✅ English:
        
        Frontend opens Razorpay payment popup (Checkout).
        
        👉 User enters:
        
        Card / UPI / Netbanking
        ✅ Tamil:
        
        Frontend-ல் Razorpay payment popup open ஆகும்
        
        👉 User:
        
        Card / UPI / Netbanking select பண்ணுவார்
        🔹 5. Payment Processing
        ✅ English:
        
        Razorpay securely processes payment with bank.
        
        ✅ Tamil:
        
        Razorpay → bank உடன் connect ஆகி payment process பண்ணும்
        
        🔹 6. Payment Success / Failure
        ✅ English:
        
        After payment:
        
        Success → payment_id generated
        Failure → error message
        ✅ Tamil:
        
        Payment முடிந்ததும்:
        
        Success → payment_id வரும்
        Failure → error வரும்
        🔹 7. Verify Payment (IMPORTANT)
        ✅ English:
        
        Backend verifies payment using:
        
        payment_id
        order_id
        signature
        
        👉 Prevents fraud
        
        ✅ Tamil:
        
        Backend-ல் payment verify பண்ணுவது மிக முக்கியம்
        
        👉 இது:
        
        fraud avoid பண்ணும்
        🔹 8. Store in Database
        ✅ English:
        
        Save:
        
        order_id
        payment_id
        status
        ✅ Tamil:
        
        Database-ல்:
        
        order_id
        payment_id
        status save பண்ணுவோம்
        🔹 9. Show Confirmation
        ✅ English:
        
        User sees:
        👉 “Payment Successful”
        
        ✅ Tamil:
        
        User-க்கு:
        👉 “Payment Successful” message காட்டப்படும்
        
        🔁 Full Flow (Simple)
        ✅ English:
        
        User → Pay → Order Create → Checkout → Payment → Verify → Store → Success
        
        ✅ Tamil:
        
        User → Pay → Order Create → Payment → Verify → Save → Success
        
        🔥 Important Concepts
        🔸 1. API Key
        Used to connect Razorpay
        🔸 2. Order ID
        Created before payment
        🔸 3. Payment ID
        Generated after payment
        🔸 4. Signature
        Used for verification (security)


